<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>This time to find the constant <span class="process-math">\(c\)</span>  we observe that since <span class="process-math">\(y(0)=2=\)</span> we have</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{equation*}
2=y(0)=\brackeval{-4.9t^2+19.6t+c}{t}{0} =c.
\end{equation*}
</div>
<p class="continuation">Thus the ball's position is given by: <span class="process-math">\(y=-4.9t^2+19.6t+2\text{.}\)</span></p>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-3.html#p-36" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
</body>
